# Symfony wrapper for Blueprint Css Framework #

The `sfBlueprintPlugin` offers helpers that integrate the [Blueprint CSS framework](http://www.blueprintcss.org/) V 0.9.1.

## Usage ##
In your application settings.yml

    [yaml]
    all:
	  .setting
	    standard_helpers:       [..., blueprint]

## Options ##
Blueprint css framework is provided with 4 plugins. You can activate them in app.yml

    [yaml]
    all:
	  blueprint:
	    plugins: [buttons,fancy-type,link-icons,rtl]
